{"title":"Ubuntu20通过Samba工具与windows系统实现文件共享传输","uid":"ea66ce5e6327d05b99157aa6cede6c50","slug":"1OS/samba","date":"2022-12-12T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2023-02-14T08:01:23.368Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/1OS/samba.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://jihulab.com/dengbowang/img/raw/main/pictures/2023/02/14_202302141509524.png","content":"<h1 id=\"Ubuntu20通过Samba工具与windows系统实现文件共享传输\"><a href=\"#Ubuntu20通过Samba工具与windows系统实现文件共享传输\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Ubuntu20通过Samba工具与windows系统实现文件共享传输\"></a>Ubuntu20通过Samba工具与windows系统实现文件共享传输</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>实测可用！！！！踩过N个坑了！！！</p>\n<p>你要是失败；那就是ubuntu系统问题；重装系统再试一遍</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"Ubuntu\"><a href=\"#Ubuntu\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Ubuntu\"></a>Ubuntu</h2><h3 id=\"1、安装samba服务器\"><a href=\"#1、安装samba服务器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1、安装samba服务器\"></a>1、安装samba服务器</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo apt-get install samba samba-common</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://jihulab.com/dengbowang/img/raw/main/pictures/2023/02/14_202302141508513.png\" alt=\"图片\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"2、配置需要共享的目录\"><a href=\"#2、配置需要共享的目录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2、配置需要共享的目录\"></a>2、配置需要共享的目录</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo chmod 777 &#x2F;home&#x2F; -R</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://jihulab.com/dengbowang/img/raw/main/pictures/2023/02/14_202302141509307.png\" alt=\"图片\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"3、添加Samba用户\"><a href=\"#3、添加Samba用户\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3、添加Samba用户\"></a>3、添加Samba用户</h3><p><img src=\"https://jihulab.com/dengbowang/img/raw/main/pictures/2023/02/14_202302141509764.png\" alt=\"图片\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"4、配置Samba（重点）\"><a href=\"#4、配置Samba（重点）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4、配置Samba（重点）\"></a>4、配置Samba（重点）</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo vi &#x2F;etc&#x2F;samba&#x2F;smb.conf</code></pre>\n\n<p>在末尾添加如下代码工作组的话查看你自己电脑的Windows下的工作组名</p>\n<p>read only &#x3D; no    &#x2F;&#x2F;就是可读可写的含义</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://jihulab.com/dengbowang/img/raw/main/pictures/2023/02/14_202302141509329.png\" alt=\"图片\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://jihulab.com/dengbowang/img/raw/main/pictures/2023/02/14_202302141509514.png\" alt=\"图片\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"5、重启samba服务\"><a href=\"#5、重启samba服务\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5、重启samba服务\"></a>5、重启samba服务</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo service smbd restart</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://jihulab.com/dengbowang/img/raw/main/pictures/2023/02/14_202302141509251.png\" alt=\"图片\"></p>\n<p>6、查看ubuntu系统IP地址 </p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">ip add</code></pre>\n<p>红色框内就是ubuntu的地址</p>\n<p>Ubuntu和windows需要在同一网段内；虚拟机设置桥接就可以了</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://jihulab.com/dengbowang/img/raw/main/pictures/2023/02/14_202302141525187.png\" alt=\"图片\"></p>\n<p>这是windows的IP地址</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://jihulab.com/dengbowang/img/raw/main/pictures/2023/02/14_202302141509738.png\" alt=\"图片\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"windows端\"><a href=\"#windows端\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"windows端\"></a>windows端</h2><p>1、资源管理器访问</p>\n<p>地址栏输入 <code>\\\\ + IP</code>地址回车就能看见ubuntu设置的共享文件夹了</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://jihulab.com/dengbowang/img/raw/main/pictures/2023/02/14_202302141509524.png\" alt=\"图片\"></p>\n<p>2、浏览器访问</p>\n<p>把资源管理器地址栏的IP和路径复制粘贴到浏览器地址栏就可以了</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://jihulab.com/dengbowang/img/raw/main/pictures/2023/02/14_202302141510028.png\" alt=\"图片\"></p>\n<hr>\n","text":"Ubuntu20通过Samba工具与windows系统实现文件共享传输 实测可用！！！！踩过N个坑了！！！ 你要是失败；那就是ubuntu系统问题；重装系统再试一遍 Ubuntu1、安装samba服务器sudo apt-get install samba samba-common...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":581,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"OS","slug":"OS","count":3,"path":"api/categories/OS.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":3,"path":"api/tags/Linux.json"},{"name":"samba","slug":"samba","count":1,"path":"api/tags/samba.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Ubuntu20%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87Samba%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E4%B8%8Ewindows%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E